hopobject.body: What do you study? perindopril 5 mg precio Mr Farage might yet stand in Great Yarmouth. But Yarmouth, Blackpool, Clacton, Margate and Rhyl are none of them the kind of “bungalow towns” filled with “self-supporting, self-reliant” people that Ukip feels are its own. If anything, these places are likely to feel increasingly alienated from the political mainstream, and if they are left to decline any further, they will become an ever‑greater burden on taxpayers.
